## 📋 Complete Test Report

### ✅ Step 1: BUG Banner Confirmed (Top of Page)
The page shows **"Adult Bronze Dragon"** (Huge Dragon, lawful good) with a prominent BUG warning banner:
- **⚠️ BUG: Actions Not Grouped By Type**
- Content: "The buggy template renders **ALL 10 actions** under a single 'Actions' heading, including **3 Legendary Actions** (Detect, Tail Attack, Wing Attack)."
- Expected: Legendary Actions should have their own separate heading
- Actual: All actions are mixed together under "Actions"

### ✅ Step 2: Buggy View - All 10 Actions Mixed Under Single "Actions" Heading
The 🔴 **Buggy View (commit c2bb6b13b9)** confirmed all 10 actions mixed together:

| # | Action | Type Tag |
