- Tail Attack
- Wing Attack

### 🐛 Bug Summary
The buggy implementation fails to group actions by `action_type`, causing all 10 actions (including 3 LEGENDARY_ACTION types) to be rendered under a single "Actions" heading without any separate "Legendary Actions" section. The fixed version (commit c856d97450) correctly separates them into "Action" and "Legendary Action" groupings.
